reviews.review_text:
One of My Favorites This was one of my favorite shows I attended. We were on the outskirts of the taper section. I remember the guy screaming to Phil for St. Stephen. Funny in a sad clown kind of way.

Crackling show. I love a good audience tape. Thank you.
